		<event name="SOCIALIZE_TRASH_EATER_TRACKER_1" req="protogen_tracker"/>
	</loadEventList>
</event>
<event name="SOCIALIZE_TRASH_EATER_NOTHING">
	<text>The Trash Eater appears to be resting in his cabin. He's standing up, completely immobile. "HEAD EMPTY. NO TRASH IN HEAD. ADD TRASH TO HEAD. PLEASE.". Perhaps it's better to leave them alone.</text>
</event>


